Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:04.21,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}It's been so long since we left our home behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:10.39,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Drifting on the Milky Way almost every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:13.97,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Where am I supposed to go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:17.14,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}What're we really looking for ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:22.44,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Stumbling in the darkness, cold and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:29.20,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}But a ray of hope still exists in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:34.62,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Rain or shine, always chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:38.62,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Someday we'll find the way to dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:42.38,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}An escape from broken space
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:47.13,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}We won't lose our way"We can hold on"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:51.01,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Even if you're against the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:52.60,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Never stop !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:54.43,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.51,0:22:59.77,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}We'll one day rise above it all (never give up)
