Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:51.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}即便逆流而上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:52.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}不要停下腳步
